WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:02.330 --> 00:00:11.840
Hello YouTubers, I am back from my vacation
and I am going to be doing more videos for

00:00:11.840 --> 00:00:12.840
you.

00:00:12.840 --> 00:00:24.020
First, I want to make some announcements,
the producers of this video series in the

00:00:24.020 --> 00:00:32.390
ashram told me that they are unable to upload
any more videos on the friend’s section

00:00:32.390 --> 00:00:44.479
for whatever reason so what is going to happen
hereafter is there will be only one channel

00:00:44.479 --> 00:00:56.369
so all my videos will be uploaded in the public
channel so that’s the first announcement.

00:00:56.369 --> 00:01:14.600
The second one is that I have a desire that
my videos should be useful for people from

00:01:14.600 --> 00:01:23.030
more than just being an intellectual entertainment.

00:01:23.030 --> 00:01:33.210
I know that the techniques that I talk about
work, they have been given to us by the Yogis

00:01:33.210 --> 00:01:47.060
and the Siddhas who have meditated hundreds
and thousands of years in order to find out

00:01:47.060 --> 00:01:56.830
what can help humanity, human suffering, illness
and so forth.

00:01:56.830 --> 00:02:14.380
So I want you to take this teachings seriously
and also make other people to know about this;

00:02:14.380 --> 00:02:27.590
up until now you may have seen that I have
never subscribed to any channel and I have

00:02:27.590 --> 00:02:33.500
never asked anyone to subscribe to my channel.

00:02:33.500 --> 00:02:44.170
But I just now decided to ask people who watch
my videos to subscribe and to rate because

00:02:44.170 --> 00:02:56.290
I understand that this would help YouTube
to make a decision to feature my videos which

00:02:56.290 --> 00:03:07.610
will allow the videos to be seen by a large
number of people.

00:03:07.610 --> 00:03:22.020
I have a number of things that I wanted to
do for the new set of video.

00:03:22.020 --> 00:03:36.989
I was in New York and I filmed some videos
with an actress just graduated from school.

00:03:36.989 --> 00:03:47.270
This to dramatically present my teachings
in appropriate contest.

00:03:47.270 --> 00:04:01.459
I think this will be useful for people who
are unable to concentrate on just a teaching

00:04:01.459 --> 00:04:13.870
video but something seen in a more lively
and entertainment oriented setting.

00:04:13.870 --> 00:04:26.499
I have made about 7 videos, all at the Central
Park in Manhattan.

00:04:26.499 --> 00:04:31.419
So this would be available, I am very delighted
about it.

00:04:31.419 --> 00:04:44.249
Also another announcement is an attempt being
made in San Francisco by my devotees to present

00:04:44.249 --> 00:04:56.009
my teachings on Astrology, also in a dramatic
contest.

00:04:56.009 --> 00:05:03.539
So these things are going to be forthcoming
and I am very happy to announce these things.

